{"tid":59772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港人港地無聲消失 梁振英：現時樓市冇過熱","createTime":"2016-12-30T02:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T12:56:14.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"266d6a5913eb4a7e1a4cfc30b3a50fbe6fe74c25","tid":59772,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:19:05.000Z","msg":"《星島日報》今日頭版報道，梁振英政府推出兩幅「港人港地」後，已經決定擱置政策。梁振英今日出席行政會議前，始終不肯直接承認政策已擱置，他指，「推出時已話（港人港地政策）係先導計劃，而且喺樓市過熱先用。」梁振英形容，樓市已經不存在過熱情況，如日後有需要，港人港地可以再啟動。<br />\n梁振英今早出席行會前主動提到，會繼續樓市發展。被問到港人港地的立法工作是否擱置，梁振英沒有正面回應，只說海外買家需求，已跌至相當低的水平，「港人港地」措施，獲市場接受，顯示政策可行，日後有需要時會在短時間內啟動，他最後不忘再補充一句，「如果有需要嘅話。」他指，租金、樓價有回落的迹象，形容樓市「不存在一個過熱的情況」。<br />\n翻查中原樓價指數的走勢，相比去年3月推出「港人港地」措施，現時樓市大約回落了2.9%。<br />\n星島：參選政綱 不明言擱置<br />\n《星島日報》今日頭版報道，去年首季推兩幅啟德土地作「港人港地」後，港府內部已決定擱置有關政策，「港人港地」立法及涉及規管執法的工作亦很繁複，港府經檢討後，認為現時無必要再推。但由於「港人港地」是梁振英參選時的重點政綱，港府亦不會明言已擱置，只強調現時推行政策的逼切性較低。<br />\n梁振英競選時提出「港人港地」，搏得一時掌聲。但他在2012年3月月當選特首後，一直避提「港人港地」，被質疑政策未有兌現。最終，他在同年9月初宣布「港人港地」政策正式出爐，去年3月推出兩幅於啟德發展區的「港人港地」拍賣。"},{"pid":"44659b6365a63d0c69f2c827583c2ee513852a5c","tid":59772,"uid":42550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:22:31.000Z","msg":"64無死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd4ab4daa78006104f02ee925c70861470992fb","tid":59772,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:22:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347fe0a3f38d934670347069dc5b0caad2f9f944","tid":59772,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:23:40.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"425862648d37793d2b2ee2b295cd1c7b50e6b3b0","tid":59772,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:24:33.000Z","msg":"梁振英不連任不代表不參選"},{"pid":"dd416a20cd9fb2f79a8fc84db5a6ba6118c5b475","tid":59772,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:24:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7b36234c6e5e57c6d688972b92be4c18d0c07e","tid":59772,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:25:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梁振英不連任不代表不參選</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3907c5bc24a5b6028848eb1e4a380be0544626","tid":59772,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:27:21.000Z","msg":"梁振英幾撚時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a052a70e8a3ffbc328080a9618e95209480d9358","tid":59772,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:29:05.000Z","msg":"跟8萬5一早無左一樣"},{"pid":"c350e8231d5e375001856575a7d2176ec9ec5049","tid":59772,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:30:31.000Z","msg":"我無講過我無僭建<br />\n我絕對無講過"},{"pid":"04b784883301bf32ba9a22cc260a99b2069e5524","tid":59772,"uid":10441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:31:14.000Z","msg":"已經唔存在啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4bcdd1b88cd01627c4e0dd6ace4023d0ecdaf6c","tid":59772,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:35:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1fcb2af59b693abc2c28477f3cc97e279f150be","tid":59772,"uid":45925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:37:17.000Z","msg":"乜能野 港人港地 呀。睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌，比大陸高價炒高投地叫 港人港地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7f39bea1bcbef1558ffdaf11ea390273cd4025","tid":59772,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:56:14.000Z","msg":"😎"}]}